N2  - An experimental methodology for examining conflict- handling behaviors is based on a two dimensional model that identifies five modes for managing conflict. A study was conducted that illustrated the potential benefits of the methodology. The availability of five choices did result in some behaviors that would have been ?hidden? in two-choice experimental games.
